{% set name = "jazal" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/jazal-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6ff63cce5fc6aedddaa509d1a3ea32ab4aff5245c6d33877b1b593cbeb210b42

build:

  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - python >=3.6

    - jazal
    - tests
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip
